      right from your panel.</p>
  </description>

  <launchable type="desktop-id">com.github.bgub.CosmicExtAppletPomodoro.desktop</launchable>

  <icon type="stock">com.github.bgub.CosmicExtAppletPomodoro</icon>

  <screenshots>
    <screenshot type="default">
